    <string name="disclosure_storage_title">File Access Disclosure</string>
    <string name="disclosure_storage_message">Hermes needs \"All Files Access\" permission to provide the following core features:\n\n• File management: The AI reads, creates, and edits files on your device based on your commands\n• Configuration storage: Save app settings, chat history, and skill plugins\n• Screenshot saving: Save screenshots for AI analysis\n\nThis app only accesses files when you initiate a command. It does not scan or upload your files in the background.\n\nBy tapping \"Agree &amp; Continue\", you will be directed to system settings to enable this permission.</string>
